OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells and a few showers this
OL,7,Fevening. Then dry overnight with long
OL,8,Fclear spells developing. Touch of
OL,9,Ffrost possible in sheltered spots.
OL,10,FWinds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA few east coast showers at
OL,13,Ffirst, otherwise a dry and largely
OL,14,Fsunny start. Some cloud develops for
OL,15,Fthe afternoon but it remains dry.
OL,16,FNorthwesterly breeze continuing to
OL,17,Fease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
