OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells Saturday, some
OL,7,Fevening rain. Overnight rain soon
OL,8,Fclearing Sunday then sunny spells and
OL,9,Fa few showers. Rather cloudy Monday
OL,10,Fwith a little rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
